{
  "name": "ClickIn360 Onboarding A \u2014 Kickoff",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow A \u2014 Kickoff\n\n**Triggers:** quote.accepted, invoice.paid, onboarding.manual_start\n\n**STEP 1** quote.accepted \u2192 records state in Supabase (waits for payment).\n\n**STEP 2** invoice.paid \u2192 if no prior run, sends welcome email with onboarding + booking links.\n\n**STEP 3** manual_start \u2192 skips gate, sends welcome immediately.\n\n**STEP 4** Create `onboarding_runs` table in ClickIn360 Supabase (see automations-setup-guide.md).\n\n**STEP 5** Ensure contact has onboarding_token (CRM: Start onboarding button generates it).",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 500,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -600,
        -100
      ],
      "id": "ac1e0aef-ea5d-46a0-a9a0-e1f55548d03d",
      "name": "INSTRUCTIONS: Onboarding A"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "ad82f928-4a37-4c77-8384-0613a10f86e8",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ],
      "id": "d0b22edf-4b36-4ef5-9f31-f0742e3b4492",
      "name": "Onboarding A Webhook",
      "webhookId": "ad82f928-4a37-4c77-8384-0613a10f86e8"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const root = $input.first().json;\nconst event = root.event;\nconst payload = root.payload || {};\nconst document = payload.document || {};\nconst invoice = payload.invoice || {};\nconst contact = payload.contact || document.contact || invoice.contact || {};\nconst contactId = payload.contact_id || contact.id || document.contact_id || invoice.contact_id;\nconst documentId = payload.document_id || document.id || invoice.quote_id || null;\nconst workspaceOwnerId = root.workspace_owner_id;\nconst idempotencyKey = documentId ? `${contactId}:${documentId}` : `${contactId}:no-quote`;\nconst crmBase = ($env.CRM_BASE_URL || 'https://www.clickin360.com').replace(/\\/$/, '');\nconst onboardingToken = payload.onboarding_token || contact.onboarding_token;\nconst onboardingUrl = onboardingToken ? `${crmBase}/onboarding/${onboardingToken}` : null;\nconst locale = contact.preferred_language === 'en' ? 'en' : 'es';\nreturn [{ json: { event, payload, document, invoice, contact, contactId, documentId, workspaceOwnerId, idempotencyKey, onboardingUrl, locale, contactEmail: contact.email, firstName: contact.first_name || 'there' } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        280,
        0
      ],
      "id": "45712079-871c-416a-be5b-f94a2257d744",
      "name": "Parse CRM Payload"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const d = $input.first().json;\nlet action = 'stop';\nlet reason = '';\n\nif (d.event === 'onboarding.manual_start') {\n  action = 'start';\n  reason = 'manual_override';\n} else if (d.event === 'quote.accepted') {\n  action = 'record_quote';\n  reason = 'quote_accepted_pending_invoice';\n} else if (d.event === 'invoice.paid') {\n  const quoteId = d.invoice?.quote_id || d.documentId;\n  if (!quoteId) {\n    action = 'start';\n    reason = 'invoice_paid_no_quote';\n  } else {\n    action = 'start';\n    reason = 'invoice_paid_with_quote';\n  }\n}\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...d, action, reason } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        560,
        0
      ],
      "id": "7188377e-56fa-47fc-9d5d-1307224ef006",
      "name": "Gate: Should Start Onboarding?"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict",
            "version": 2
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "e28cd99c-627b-403e-b06d-9ac9eaeef934",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.action }}",
              "rightValue": "record_quote",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        840,
        200
      ],
      "id": "e0d6d9ce-803d-4052-a8d4-a6706d6ed9da",
      "name": "IF Record Quote Accepted?"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const d = $('Gate: Should Start Onboarding?').first().json;\nreturn [{ json: {\n  idempotency_key: d.idempotencyKey,\n  contact_id: String(d.contactId),\n  document_id: d.documentId ? String(d.documentId) : null,\n  workspace_owner_id: String(d.workspaceOwnerId),\n  status: 'quote_accepted',\n  quote_accepted_at: new Date().toISOString(),\n} }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1120,
